{"ts":"2026-06-09T19:00:51.740Z","author":"codex","op":"note_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-09T19:00:51.740Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes","value":[{"created_at":"2026-06-09T19:00:51.740Z","author":"codex","text":"Implemented pi coding-agent todo state import/export as --format todojson. The format accepts upstream TodoDetails { action, todos, nextId } or a raw Todo[] array, maps text/done to pm title/status, defaults todojson import to upsert so repeated imports do not duplicate pm items, and exports TodoDetails JSON with sequential ids. Removed redundant explicit todos import/export command registrations so native importer/exporter routes no longer self-collide in pm package doctor. Verified no credential-shaped secrets in package-owned source/history; npm pack allowlist contains only dist/docs/manifest/package metadata."}]}],"before_hash":"965579b0f1637558eab9ec502c3df9f5f246893396adb57dca1285f8e7f9d40b","after_hash":"053538b61b5c460034ffcdccc0adb211810e95d044294ba8e371805cb477a2c0"}
